value_i18n.ar_SA:
The goal of the Campaign in a Box (CIAB) program is to help our partners generate demand and drive high quality leads for Liferay solutions by providing a customizable marketing toolkit for launching a marketing campaign.

Partners can select which campaign assets (provided as Adobe Acrobat PDF files) to use and launch to find new and high quality leads. Note: It may be possible for partners can use their annual MDF allocation for their lead generation activities in conjunction with the Campaign in a Box toolkit. Please contact your Partner Marketing Manager for more information.
